# wpa_supplicant.conf helpers

## Parse wpa_supplicant.conf and create db-wpa_supplicant_conf.yml

The parsing works with the blocks separated by an empty line. See the
example wpa_supplicant.conf

```console
shell > ansible-playbook pb-parse-wpa_supplicant_conf.yml -e debug=true
```

```yaml
PLAY [Parse wpa_supplicant.conf] ************************************************************************************

TASK [Read wpa_supplicant.conf] *************************************************************************************
changed: [localhost]

TASK [ansible.builtin.debug] ****************************************************************************************
ok: [localhost] => 
    data:
    - |-
        ctrl_interface=/run/wpa_supplicant
        ctrl_interface_group=adm
        fast_reauth=0
        update_config=1
    - |-
        network={
                ssid="TEST"
                psk="password"
                pairwise=CCMP
                mesh_fwding=1
                disabled=1
        }
    - |-
        network={
                ssid="TEST 2"
                psk="my password"
                pairwise=CCMP
                mesh_fwding=1
                disabled=1
        }

TASK [Create configuration file db-wpa_supplicat_conf.yml] **********************************************************
ok: [localhost]

PLAY RECAP **********************************************************************************************************
localhost                  : ok=3    changed=1    unreachable=0    failed=0    skipped=0    rescued=0    ignored=0
```

## Create wpa_supplicant.conf.new from db-wpa_supplicate_conf.yml

The variables db_wpa_supplicant_conf and db_wpa_supplicant_conf_common
work with the template wpa-supplicant.conf-v3.j2

```console
shell > ansible-playbook pb-wpa_supplicant_conf.yml -e debug=true
```

```yaml
PLAY [Create wpa_supplicant.conf.new] *******************************************************************************

TASK [Debug db_wpa_supplicant_conf] *********************************************************************************
ok: [localhost] => 
    msg: |-
        db_wpa_supplicant_conf_common:
          ctrl_interface: /run/wpa_supplicant
          ctrl_interface_group: adm
          fast_reauth: 0
          update_config: 1

        db_wpa_supplicant_conf:
          - {disabled: 1, mesh_fwding: 1, pairwise: CCMP, psk: password, ssid: TEST}
          - {disabled: 1, mesh_fwding: 1, pairwise: CCMP, psk: my password, ssid: TEST 2}

TASK [Create wpa_supplicant.conf.new] *******************************************************************************
changed: [localhost]

PLAY RECAP **********************************************************************************************************
localhost                  : ok=2    changed=1    unreachable=0    failed=0    skipped=0    rescued=0    ignored=0   
```
